sequenceDiagram
    participant Mobile
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant Storage
    participant PG as PaymentGateway

    Mobile->>API: POST /events/{event}/purchase
    API->>DB: BEGIN + lock ticket_type
    DB-->>API: lock ok
    API->>DB: increment sold, create order+order_item
    DB-->>API: COMMIT
    API-->>Mobile: 201 {order_id}

    Mobile->>API: POST /orders/{order}/payment/qris
    API->>API: generate QRIS, write PNG
    API->>Storage: put private/payments/{order}.png
    API-->>Mobile: 200 {qr_url (signed)}

    Mobile->>Storage: GET signed qr_url
    Storage-->>Mobile: image/png

    Mobile->>PG: user scans & pays
    PG-->>API: (webhook) payment success
    API->>DB: BEGIN
    API->>DB: if order.pending -> update status=paid, paid_at
    API->>DB: create ticket records
    API->>Storage: write ticket QR images
    DB-->>API: COMMIT
    API-->>Mobile: payment status=paid
